{"_path":"/city/t024","_dir":"city","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"震後安居3計畫","description":null,"image":"/images/city/t024-1.jpeg","sequence":24,"category":"災難救濟","author":"住宅發展處","link":"https://www.facebook.com/sun0976315743/posts/pfbid032r9X64eqMFtw7mSuW44n3uusX79bekCj6VTTw65YethMtfXi6GNu89eGctfj6dfpl","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-04-19T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"震後安居-3-計畫"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"震後安居 3 計畫"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園簡化震後修繕程序，補助居全台最高 👍"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n自 0403 地震影響，至今仍然餘震不斷，為快速幫助受災戶重建家園！#張善政市長 提出 👉🏻 簡化震後修繕程序計畫，讓繁瑣的修繕流程，變得簡單且更快速又方便！唯有重視市民的居住品質，才能讓市民更安心 🩷"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"📝 震後修繕安居三計畫 👇🏻"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1️⃣ 合法建物修繕補助 🏠"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"紅單全額補助，最高 150 萬 💰"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"黃單 85%補助，最高 100 萬 💰"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2️⃣ 公寓大廈修繕補助 🏠"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"若是公寓大廈，不管是否受地震影響！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"只要符合資格皆🉑提出申請，並針對有修繕必要的地方進行補強，補助額度最高 🆙2000 萬（此項補助金額，將會依社規模設定級距而定）"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3️⃣ 簡易都更整維計畫 🏠"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"針對建物受損程度未及紅、黃單，或過去已受損害卻沒機會補強的建物進行補助！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"只要管理委員會取得全數住戶同意，便可申請 ▶️ 外牆拉皮+耐震補強！此流程也會精簡行政程序，直接將申請案件送審議委員會進行審議！補助額度也調整至 75%，上限 1500 萬元 💰"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"期盼透過震後修繕安居三計畫 💪\n讓民眾積極檢視家中建物的安全問題！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n市府陪您一起度過震後的艱難時刻，讓民眾在震後能夠盡快恢復正常生活，不再為地震而擔心受怕 😉\n想了解更多簡化震後修繕程序，桃園安居三計畫，請至桃園市政府住宅發展處查詢 🔍\n🔗"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ohd.tycg.gov.tw/News_Content.aspx?n=8601&s=1272109","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"https://ohd.tycg.gov.tw/News_Content.aspx?n=8601&s=1272109"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"t024-1.jpeg","src":"/images/city/t024-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"震後安居-3-計畫","depth":2,"text":"震後安居 3 計畫"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:city:t024.md","_source":"content","_file":"city/t024.md","_extension":"md"}